file: SymfonyPlatformInvoker.php
class: "Ineersa\\AgentCore\\Infrastructure\\SymfonyAi\\SymfonyPlatformInvoker"
type: readonly final class
summary: "SymfonyPlatformInvoker acts as an adapter for the Symfony AI platform, translating generic agent inputs into platform-specific invocations. It handles the execution of model calls and extracts structured usage metadata from the platform's deferred results."
